<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What you'll learn</h2>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">For service managers</h3>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>How <a href="https://www.planx.uk/" class="govuk-link">PlanX</a> structures planning flows with a visual editor</li>
      <li>How citizens experience the planning application journey</li>
      <li>The flow editor's drag-and-drop interface for non-technical users</li>
      <li>How flows map to planning policy and legislation</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-half">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">For technical staff</h3>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>ECS Fargate deployment with Aurora PostgreSQL</li>
      <li>React/Vite editor with Node.js API and Hasura GraphQL</li>
      <li>ShareDB real-time collaboration layer</li>
      <li>CloudFront HTTPS with S3 static asset hosting</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What's included</h2>

<p class="govuk-body">
  Your deployment comes pre-loaded with:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li><strong>NDX Demo Council team</strong> with sample planning flows ready to explore</li>
  <li><strong>Householder planning application flow</strong> — the most common planning application type</li>
  <li><strong>Lawful Development Certificate flow</strong> — for proposed or existing development</li>
  <li><strong>Drag-and-drop flow editor</strong> — create and modify flows without writing code</li>
  <li><strong>Hasura GraphQL console</strong> — explore the data model and run queries</li>
</ul>

<p class="govuk-body">
  <a href="https://www.planx.uk/" class="govuk-link">Learn more about PlanX on the Open Digital Planning website</a>
</p>

